### Patient Management Service — Doctor Endpoints
### Requires: REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Only "admin" role can create, update, or deactivate doctors.
### All authenticated users can read.
###
### IMPORTANT: You need a valid specialtyId before creating a doctor.
###            Run specialties.http first to create a specialty and get its UUID.

@baseUrl     = http://localhost:8001
@token       = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI5MWI0YTg5OC0wNDkxLTRlOGMtODMxZS04ZTBmNzgzMjNiOGYiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGNoaXJpbW95YS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJ0eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzg0MzM5ODUxLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQzMzg5NTF9.3QE6_kx9pgUb1RxC2xPdUOHkD_GDtLe-0AV9hPId7yM
@adminToken  = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI5MWI0YTg5OC0wNDkxLTRlOGMtODMxZS04ZTBmNzgzMjNiOGYiLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGNoaXJpbW95YS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJ0eXBlIjoiYWNjZXNzIiwiZXhwIjoxNzg0MzM5ODUxLCJpYXQiOjE3ODQzMzg5NTF9.3QE6_kx9pgUb1RxC2xPdUOHkD_GDtLe-0AV9hPId7yM
@doctorId    = PASTE_DOCTOR_UUID_HERE
@employeeId  = PASTE_EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE
@specialtyId = PASTE_SPECIALTY_UUID_HERE


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# POST /api/v1/doctors  — Register a new doctor (admin only)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Create doctor — minimal required fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "first_name": "Ana",
  "last_name": "Ramírez",
  "specialty_id": "{{specialtyId}}"
}

###

### 2. Create doctor — full payload with all optional fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "first_name": "Roberto",
  "last_name": "Herrera",
  "date_of_birth": "1975-08-14",
  "gender": "male",
  "specialty_id": "{{specialtyId}}",
  "years_of_experience": 18,
  "bio": "Board-certified cardiologist with 18 years of experience in interventional cardiology.",
  "license_info": {
    "license_number": "FL-MED-2025-001234",
    "issuing_body": "Florida Board of Medicine",
    "issue_date": "2005-06-01",
    "expiration_date": "2027-06-01",
    "state": "FL"
  },
  "contact_info": {
    "phone_number": "+1-305-555-7890",
    "email": "dr.herrera@chirimoya.com"
  },
  "address": {
    "street_line_1": "789 Medical Center Drive",
    "street_line_2": "Suite 300",
    "city": "Miami",
    "state": "FL",
    "postal_code": "33136",
    "country": "US"
  }
}

###

### 3. Create doctor — expect 404 Not Found (invalid specialty_id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "first_name": "Ghost",
  "last_name": "Doctor",
  "specialty_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### 4. Create doctor — expect 403 Forbidden (non-admin token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "first_name": "Unauthorized",
  "last_name": "Doctor",
  "specialty_id": "{{specialtyId}}"
}

###

### 5. Create doctor — expect 401 Unauthorized (missing token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "No",
  "last_name": "Token",
  "specialty_id": "{{specialtyId}}"
}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GET /api/v1/doctors  — Search / list doctors
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 6. List all doctors — default pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Search by first name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors?first_name=Ana
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 8. Search by last name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors?last_name=Herrera
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Filter by specialty_id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors?specialty_id={{specialtyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 10. Filter by status (active | inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 11. Search with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors?limit=5&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 12. Combined search — name + specialty + status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors?last_name=Herrera&status=active&limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 13. Search doctors — expect 401 Unauthorized (missing token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GET /api/v1/doctors/{doctor_id}  — Get doctor by UUID
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 14. Get doctor by UUID — replace doctorId at the top
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 15. Get doctor by UUID — expect 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GET /api/v1/doctors/emp/{employee_id}  — Get doctor by Employee ID
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 16. Get doctor by employee ID — replace employeeId at the top
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/emp/{{employeeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 17. Get doctor by employee ID — expect 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/emp/EMP-DOES-NOT-EXIST
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PATCH /api/v1/doctors/{doctor_id}  — Partial update (admin only)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 18. Update doctor bio and years of experience
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "bio": "Updated: Specializes in advanced cardiac imaging and minimally invasive procedures.",
  "years_of_experience": 20
}

###

### 19. Update doctor contact info
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "contact_info": {
    "phone_number": "+1-305-555-0000",
    "email": "dr.herrera.updated@chirimoya.com"
  }
}

###

### 20. Update doctor license
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "license_info": {
    "license_number": "FL-MED-2026-001234",
    "issuing_body": "Florida Board of Medicine",
    "issue_date": "2005-06-01",
    "expiration_date": "2028-06-01",
    "state": "FL"
  }
}

###

### 21. Change doctor specialty
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "specialty_id": "{{specialtyId}}"
}

###

### 22. Update doctor — expect 404 Not Found
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "bio": "Ghost doctor"
}

###

### 23. Update doctor — expect 403 Forbidden (non-admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bio": "Should be rejected."
}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DELETE /api/v1/doctors/{doctor_id}  — Deactivate (soft-delete, admin only)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

###

### 24. Deactivate doctor — sets status=inactive
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 25. Deactivate doctor — expect 404 Not Found
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 26. Deactivate doctor — expect 403 Forbidden (non-admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/doctors/{{doctorId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
